WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.964 align:middle line:90%


00:00:00.964 --> 00:00:03.940 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:00:03.940 --> 00:00:36.750 align:middle line:90%


00:00:36.750 --> 00:00:38.510 align:middle line:90%
>>Newspapers talked about it.

00:00:38.510 --> 00:00:40.710 align:middle line:90%
People wanted to know.

00:00:40.710 --> 00:00:43.220 align:middle line:84%
But nobody could
penetrate the mystery.

00:00:43.220 --> 00:00:45.270 align:middle line:90%
What was going on?

00:00:45.270 --> 00:00:49.740 align:middle line:84%
Strange flying machines were
flying the skies of Italy.

00:00:49.740 --> 00:00:53.110 align:middle line:90%
It was the '50s.

00:00:53.110 --> 00:00:55.570 align:middle line:84%
Some people took
incredible photos.

00:00:55.570 --> 00:00:58.170 align:middle line:84%
Others were frightened
and shouted, they're here.

00:00:58.170 --> 00:00:59.910 align:middle line:90%
They're among us.

00:00:59.910 --> 00:01:03.490 align:middle line:84%
While still others believed
the aliens had come to help.

00:01:03.490 --> 00:01:05.180 align:middle line:90%
But who were they?

00:01:05.180 --> 00:01:06.720 align:middle line:90%
Where were they from?

00:01:06.720 --> 00:01:09.760 align:middle line:90%
Above all, what did they want?

00:01:09.760 --> 00:01:12.840 align:middle line:84%
Many knew but kept
quiet, a mystery that

00:01:12.840 --> 00:01:15.240 align:middle line:84%
has remained as
such for decades,

00:01:15.240 --> 00:01:18.730 align:middle line:84%
a secret now
revealed-- Friendship,

00:01:18.730 --> 00:01:22.630 align:middle line:84%
the incredible story of
mass contact between humans

00:01:22.630 --> 00:01:25.542 align:middle line:90%
and extraterrestrials.

00:01:25.542 --> 00:01:29.000 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:38.390 align:middle line:90%


00:01:38.390 --> 00:01:41.475 align:middle line:10%
Until recently, the
phenomenon of contactism,

00:01:41.475 --> 00:01:45.420 align:middle line:10%
or the deliberate encounter
repeated over time between man

00:01:45.420 --> 00:01:48.240 align:middle line:10%
and evolved
extraterrestrial entities,

00:01:48.240 --> 00:01:51.660 align:middle line:10%
was believed to involve only
a few chosen individuals

00:01:51.660 --> 00:01:54.080 align:middle line:10%
or contactees.

00:01:54.080 --> 00:01:58.430 align:middle line:84%
Many of them went down in
history-- George Adamski,

00:01:58.430 --> 00:02:03.270 align:middle line:84%
Howard Menger, Eugenio
Siragusa, just to name a few.

00:02:03.270 --> 00:02:07.060 align:middle line:84%
All of them faithfully
abided by this cliche.

00:02:07.060 --> 00:02:09.690 align:middle line:84%
But in 2007, something
happened that would

00:02:09.690 --> 00:02:12.220 align:middle line:90%
change the cards on the table.

00:02:12.220 --> 00:02:16.230 align:middle line:84%
Stefano Breccia, an engineer
from Marche living in Abruzzo,

00:02:16.230 --> 00:02:19.870 align:middle line:84%
published some
startling papers that

00:02:19.870 --> 00:02:23.240 align:middle line:84%
seemed to reveal the story
of repeated direct encounters

00:02:23.240 --> 00:02:27.810 align:middle line:84%
between more than 100 people and
extraterrestrial beings living

00:02:27.810 --> 00:02:30.342 align:middle line:84%
in numerous secret
bases on our planet.

00:02:30.342 --> 00:02:33.440 align:middle line:90%


00:02:33.440 --> 00:02:36.470 align:middle line:84%
The main figure of the event
told by Breccia is the writer

00:02:36.470 --> 00:02:38.670 align:middle line:90%
Bruno Sammaccicia .

00:02:38.670 --> 00:02:40.920 align:middle line:84%
The case is said to
have taken place mainly

00:02:40.920 --> 00:02:43.620 align:middle line:90%
in and around Pescara.

00:02:43.620 --> 00:02:50.330 align:middle line:84%
It would all begin in 1956
and would last for many years.

00:02:50.330 --> 00:02:53.300 align:middle line:84%
The film clips and photographs
that have emerged so far

00:02:53.300 --> 00:02:55.130 align:middle line:90%
are of considerable interest.

00:02:55.130 --> 00:02:57.470 align:middle line:84%
But even more extraordinary
are the testimonies

00:02:57.470 --> 00:03:01.310 align:middle line:90%
of the individuals involved.

00:03:01.310 --> 00:03:04.180 align:middle line:84%
Everyone called their
story Friendship.

00:03:04.180 --> 00:03:08.420 align:middle line:84%
And that is the name that
has come down to us today.

00:03:08.420 --> 00:03:10.430 align:middle line:84%
Thanks to Stefano
Breccia's courage,

00:03:10.430 --> 00:03:13.330 align:middle line:84%
one of the most awe-inspiring
sagas in ufology

00:03:13.330 --> 00:03:15.040 align:middle line:90%
has come to light.

00:03:15.040 --> 00:03:18.520 align:middle line:84%
It wasn't an easy decision
to decide to make it known.

00:03:18.520 --> 00:03:24.790 align:middle line:10%
It all started from an
idea by Bruno Sammaccicia .

00:03:24.790 --> 00:03:29.170 align:middle line:84%
He'd been thinking about
writing down his experiences

00:03:29.170 --> 00:03:32.820 align:middle line:84%
and then asked me to
be the one to do it.

00:03:32.820 --> 00:03:39.570 align:middle line:84%
And so I was at his house for
a month to record his stories.

00:03:39.570 --> 00:03:43.830 align:middle line:90%
Then I put everything together.

00:03:43.830 --> 00:03:46.370 align:middle line:84%
>>Besides granting his
dear friend's wishes,

00:03:46.370 --> 00:03:50.170 align:middle line:84%
Breccia had set himself
another objective.

00:03:50.170 --> 00:03:52.680 align:middle line:84%
>>One reason is to
hope that it might

00:03:52.680 --> 00:03:57.010 align:middle line:84%
work as bait to encourage
other people in the group

00:03:57.010 --> 00:03:59.190 align:middle line:90%
to come forward.

00:03:59.190 --> 00:04:01.930 align:middle line:84%
>>Gaspare De Lama
and his wife Mirella

00:04:01.930 --> 00:04:03.850 align:middle line:84%
are among those
still alive today

00:04:03.850 --> 00:04:06.430 align:middle line:84%
who were involved in
the Friendship events

00:04:06.430 --> 00:04:09.105 align:middle line:84%
and who accepted Breccia's
invitation to come forward.

00:04:09.105 --> 00:04:13.810 align:middle line:90%


00:04:13.810 --> 00:04:16.880 align:middle line:84%
They now live on the
shores of Lake Como.

00:04:16.880 --> 00:04:19.370 align:middle line:84%
Gaspare admired
Stefano's courage

00:04:19.370 --> 00:04:22.160 align:middle line:84%
to expose himself so
directly, despite being

00:04:22.160 --> 00:04:24.556 align:middle line:84%
a well-known figure in
science and academia.

00:04:24.556 --> 00:04:27.750 align:middle line:90%


00:04:27.750 --> 00:04:30.450 align:middle line:10%
>>He had no hesitation
about exposing himself,

00:04:30.450 --> 00:04:32.110 align:middle line:10%
and I admired him for that.

00:04:32.110 --> 00:04:38.020 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:04:38.020 --> 00:04:41.260 align:middle line:84%
>>And so coming out and talking
about my experience becomes

00:04:41.260 --> 00:04:45.010 align:middle line:84%
easy for me because it
gives me great joy--

00:04:45.010 --> 00:04:49.940 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:04:49.940 --> 00:04:52.620 align:middle line:84%
>> --the joy of being able to
tell people something that can

00:04:52.620 --> 00:04:56.300 align:middle line:84%
help them understand more
or make their doubts grow

00:04:56.300 --> 00:04:59.680 align:middle line:84%
or disappear or
strengthen their belief.

00:04:59.680 --> 00:05:03.880 align:middle line:10%
>>Gaspare De Lama became a fan
of ufology in the late '40s

00:05:03.880 --> 00:05:06.350 align:middle line:10%
and, together with his
wife, sought a path

00:05:06.350 --> 00:05:08.680 align:middle line:10%
to greater awareness.

00:05:08.680 --> 00:05:12.837 align:middle line:84%
Even Gaspare's mother
took part in the events.

00:05:12.837 --> 00:05:13.670 align:middle line:10%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:05:13.670 --> 00:05:20.150 align:middle line:10%
>>Gaspare, his mother
Zita, and I had--

00:05:20.150 --> 00:05:21.100 align:middle line:10%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:05:21.100 --> 00:05:26.690 align:middle line:84%
>> --finally achieved our goal,
which was to get to know them.

00:05:26.690 --> 00:05:29.600 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:05:29.600 --> 00:05:32.540 align:middle line:84%
>>We were hoping
for an experience

00:05:32.540 --> 00:05:37.990 align:middle line:84%
with teachers who
could help us improve.

00:05:37.990 --> 00:05:41.070 align:middle line:84%
>>In the Friendship story,
Sammaccicia called the beings

00:05:41.070 --> 00:05:44.670 align:middle line:90%
by the name of W56.

00:05:44.670 --> 00:05:46.780 align:middle line:84%
They weren't a single
race but a group

00:05:46.780 --> 00:05:49.760 align:middle line:84%
of extraterrestrial beings
coming from different parts

00:05:49.760 --> 00:05:52.940 align:middle line:90%
of the universe.

00:05:52.940 --> 00:05:54.522 align:middle line:84%
Although they
looked like humans,

00:05:54.522 --> 00:05:55.980 align:middle line:84%
there were considerable
differences

00:05:55.980 --> 00:06:00.680 align:middle line:84%
in height, which ranged
from 1 to 6 meters.

00:06:00.680 --> 00:06:06.420 align:middle line:84%
The first encounter took
place in April 1956.

00:06:06.420 --> 00:06:09.700 align:middle line:84%
Bruno Sammaccicia was there,
along with his two friends,

00:06:09.700 --> 00:06:13.040 align:middle line:90%
Giancarlo and Julio.

00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:14.500 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:06:14.500 --> 00:06:17.060 align:middle line:10%
>>Bruno said that an
old friend had given him

00:06:17.060 --> 00:06:20.730 align:middle line:10%
this parchment because
Bruno collected antiques.

00:06:20.730 --> 00:06:22.735 align:middle line:10%
And while looking
at it, they noticed

00:06:22.735 --> 00:06:25.235 align:middle line:10%
it was a map of the castle above
Ascoli Piceno at Rocca Pia.

00:06:25.235 --> 00:06:28.430 align:middle line:90%


00:06:28.430 --> 00:06:31.090 align:middle line:84%
It seemed to be a
kind of treasure map.

00:06:31.090 --> 00:06:35.630 align:middle line:84%
So they decided to go and
take a look at the area.

00:06:35.630 --> 00:06:36.640 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:06:36.640 --> 00:06:39.970 align:middle line:10%
>>They went there more than once
without ever finding anything

00:06:39.970 --> 00:06:43.560 align:middle line:10%
in particular until
one night when

00:06:43.560 --> 00:06:46.030 align:middle line:10%
they came across these people.

00:06:46.030 --> 00:06:48.590 align:middle line:84%
At a certain point,
these two came out

00:06:48.590 --> 00:06:52.140 align:middle line:84%
from a path that runs
around the castle,

00:06:52.140 --> 00:06:56.340 align:middle line:84%
introduced themselves,
and started to talk.

00:06:56.340 --> 00:07:01.940 align:middle line:84%
One of them was particularly
short, about 1 meter in height,

00:07:01.940 --> 00:07:06.170 align:middle line:84%
and the other, extremely
tall, 2.5 meters,

00:07:06.170 --> 00:07:07.970 align:middle line:90%
something like that.

00:07:07.970 --> 00:07:12.510 align:middle line:84%
As for the rest, they
looked like normal people.

00:07:12.510 --> 00:07:15.730 align:middle line:84%
>>But what happened
in that encounter?

00:07:15.730 --> 00:07:18.420 align:middle line:84%
According to the
eyewitnesses, the two aliens

00:07:18.420 --> 00:07:20.990 align:middle line:90%
spoke perfect Italian.

00:07:20.990 --> 00:07:22.690 align:middle line:84%
The thing that
immediately struck them

00:07:22.690 --> 00:07:24.500 align:middle line:84%
was the strong
sense of love that

00:07:24.500 --> 00:07:27.100 align:middle line:90%
emanated from these beings.

00:07:27.100 --> 00:07:30.740 align:middle line:84%
The information they gave to
Bruno, Giancarlo, and Julio

00:07:30.740 --> 00:07:33.790 align:middle line:90%
was awesome to say the least.

00:07:33.790 --> 00:07:37.440 align:middle line:84%
They said that Earth had been
created for a positive purpose

00:07:37.440 --> 00:07:41.120 align:middle line:84%
and that man was turning
everything into evil,

00:07:41.120 --> 00:07:42.890 align:middle line:84%
that the morality
level of humans

00:07:42.890 --> 00:07:45.440 align:middle line:90%
was much lower than their own.

00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:48.000 align:middle line:10%
They explained that this
is a very critical moment

00:07:48.000 --> 00:07:49.810 align:middle line:10%
in human history.

00:07:49.810 --> 00:07:52.280 align:middle line:84%
Atomic weapons are
capable of destroying

00:07:52.280 --> 00:07:55.720 align:middle line:84%
the planet in a matter of
minutes, a tremendous risk that

00:07:55.720 --> 00:07:58.140 align:middle line:84%
could come to pass because
of our low moral sense.

00:07:58.140 --> 00:08:01.110 align:middle line:90%


00:08:01.110 --> 00:08:04.490 align:middle line:84%
Their task was to ensure that
the situation didn't get out

00:08:04.490 --> 00:08:06.030 align:middle line:90%
of hand.

00:08:06.030 --> 00:08:09.160 align:middle line:84%
They said they weren't here to
conquer, as there was nothing

00:08:09.160 --> 00:08:12.320 align:middle line:84%
to conquer, that everything
stemmed from the need

00:08:12.320 --> 00:08:14.900 align:middle line:84%
for love and respect,
and that everything

00:08:14.900 --> 00:08:17.710 align:middle line:90%
should be done in accordance.

00:08:17.710 --> 00:08:20.670 align:middle line:84%
They knew Earth's history,
philosophies, and religions

00:08:20.670 --> 00:08:22.660 align:middle line:90%
perfectly.

00:08:22.660 --> 00:08:25.700 align:middle line:84%
They said they'd already been
on Earth for many centuries,

00:08:25.700 --> 00:08:30.350 align:middle line:84%
living at secret bases in
various places on the planet.

00:08:30.350 --> 00:08:32.760 align:middle line:84%
They preferred not to
reveal themselves publicly

00:08:32.760 --> 00:08:36.010 align:middle line:84%
because people weren't
ready for the contact.

00:08:36.010 --> 00:08:39.419 align:middle line:84%
They expected a positive
return from their activity.

00:08:39.419 --> 00:08:42.159 align:middle line:84%
Their goodness and their
truth would be stronger

00:08:42.159 --> 00:08:45.030 align:middle line:90%
than human doubts.

00:08:45.030 --> 00:08:47.690 align:middle line:84%
When they left, it was
almost 3:00 in the morning.

00:08:47.690 --> 00:08:53.340 align:middle line:90%


00:08:53.340 --> 00:08:55.510 align:middle line:84%
The extraordinary
experience of Friendship

00:08:55.510 --> 00:08:58.330 align:middle line:90%
began at that very moment.

00:08:58.330 --> 00:09:02.730 align:middle line:84%
The meetings between Bruno,
Giancarlo, Julio, and the W56,

00:09:02.730 --> 00:09:07.130 align:middle line:84%
also known as the Friends,
continued for several months.

00:09:07.130 --> 00:09:10.220 align:middle line:84%
During frequent long walks
on the beach in Pescara,

00:09:10.220 --> 00:09:15.080 align:middle line:84%
they gave the humans a good
deal of other information.

00:09:15.080 --> 00:09:17.310 align:middle line:84%
Dimpietro was the
name of the captain

00:09:17.310 --> 00:09:21.980 align:middle line:84%
of the extraterrestrial
group operating in Italy.

00:09:21.980 --> 00:09:29.160 align:middle line:84%
Sigir, Sigis, Itaho, Kenio,
Sinas, Saju, Meredir, Romulus

00:09:29.160 --> 00:09:31.190 align:middle line:84%
are some of the names
that became common

00:09:31.190 --> 00:09:33.320 align:middle line:90%
within Friendship.

00:09:33.320 --> 00:09:36.700 align:middle line:84%
They were invented by the
humans because the W56 had

00:09:36.700 --> 00:09:38.070 align:middle line:90%
a different concept for names.

00:09:38.070 --> 00:09:40.930 align:middle line:90%


00:09:40.930 --> 00:09:44.706 align:middle line:84%
One of the most impressive
facts regarded their bases.

00:09:44.706 --> 00:09:46.580 align:middle line:84%
They said they had a
number of them scattered

00:09:46.580 --> 00:09:48.930 align:middle line:90%
around Italy and the world.

00:09:48.930 --> 00:09:52.760 align:middle line:84%
Their most important European
base was right in Italy.

00:09:52.760 --> 00:09:57.900 align:middle line:84%
And one of the entrances
was in fact at Rocca Pia.

00:09:57.900 --> 00:09:59.210 align:middle line:10%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:09:59.210 --> 00:10:00.010 align:middle line:10%


00:10:00.010 --> 00:10:02.330 align:middle line:10%
>>The main one was
the enormous base

00:10:02.330 --> 00:10:05.510 align:middle line:10%
at the depths of
the Adriatic, almost

00:10:05.510 --> 00:10:10.520 align:middle line:10%
in contact with the continental
shelf, which roughly ranged

00:10:10.520 --> 00:10:16.010 align:middle line:10%
from Fortuna to Rimini, as
the expanse of its longitude,

00:10:16.010 --> 00:10:20.500 align:middle line:10%
and in the latitude, went from
the middle of the Adriatic

00:10:20.500 --> 00:10:26.250 align:middle line:10%
to the Apennines, with an
upper limit of 300 meters,

00:10:26.250 --> 00:10:30.310 align:middle line:10%
so vast that it was
affected by normal weather.

00:10:30.310 --> 00:10:34.800 align:middle line:84%
So at times it
also rained inside.

00:10:34.800 --> 00:10:40.320 align:middle line:84%
Then they had many smaller
bases, closer to the surface.

00:10:40.320 --> 00:10:46.490 align:middle line:84%
There was one in Pineto, one in
Ascoli, three around Pescara,

00:10:46.490 --> 00:10:51.930 align:middle line:84%
one near Como, one in the
Milan area, and so on.

00:10:51.930 --> 00:10:55.426 align:middle line:84%
Many of them were genuine
centers of support.

00:10:55.426 --> 00:10:59.920 align:middle line:84%
But the aliens also explained
how they built their bases.

00:10:59.920 --> 00:11:02.860 align:middle line:84%
In the stories told by
Bruno, Giancarlo, and Julio,

00:11:02.860 --> 00:11:04.910 align:middle line:84%
you're immediately
aware of the huge gap

00:11:04.910 --> 00:11:08.480 align:middle line:84%
in scientific and technological
development between humans

00:11:08.480 --> 00:11:09.547 align:middle line:90%
and the Friends.

00:11:09.547 --> 00:11:10.380 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:11:10.380 --> 00:11:11.920 align:middle line:90%
>>They weren't built by digging.

00:11:11.920 --> 00:11:14.930 align:middle line:84%
But through a
particular mechanism,

00:11:14.930 --> 00:11:18.040 align:middle line:84%
they were able to compress
material laterally.

00:11:18.040 --> 00:11:20.850 align:middle line:84%
The soil would thicken
into what would later

00:11:20.850 --> 00:11:23.150 align:middle line:90%
become the walls of the place.

00:11:23.150 --> 00:11:25.830 align:middle line:84%
And then the outer
structure was formed

00:11:25.830 --> 00:11:30.720 align:middle line:84%
by extremely dense and therefore
extremely strong material.

00:11:30.720 --> 00:11:34.210 align:middle line:84%
The funny thing was that
it was very unstable.

00:11:34.210 --> 00:11:37.610 align:middle line:84%
But it always had
to be kept standing.

00:11:37.610 --> 00:11:41.550 align:middle line:84%
All you had to do was flip
a switch and everything

00:11:41.550 --> 00:11:44.570 align:middle line:90%
returned to the initial state.

00:11:44.570 --> 00:11:47.670 align:middle line:84%
So for them to open
and close a base

00:11:47.670 --> 00:11:50.890 align:middle line:84%
was a very
commonplace operation.

00:11:50.890 --> 00:11:55.327 align:middle line:84%
>>The same system was used to
create the entry corridors.

00:11:55.327 --> 00:11:56.160 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:11:56.160 --> 00:11:58.430 align:middle line:84%
>>Even the bases
closer to the surface

00:11:58.430 --> 00:12:00.870 align:middle line:90%
didn't have stable entrances.

00:12:00.870 --> 00:12:03.640 align:middle line:84%
When they had to enter,
they opened a corridor

00:12:03.640 --> 00:12:04.980 align:middle line:90%
and then closed it again.

00:12:04.980 --> 00:12:11.290 align:middle line:90%


00:12:11.290 --> 00:12:13.640 align:middle line:10%
>>Aside from the facts
related to Friendship,

00:12:13.640 --> 00:12:16.070 align:middle line:10%
the presence of secret
extraterrestrial bases

00:12:16.070 --> 00:12:19.150 align:middle line:10%
on our planet is a subject that
scholars have long been aware

00:12:19.150 --> 00:12:23.290 align:middle line:10%
of, just as there have been
numerous cases of contact

00:12:23.290 --> 00:12:27.740 align:middle line:10%
throughout the world, like
the one the American policeman

00:12:27.740 --> 00:12:29.580 align:middle line:10%
named Herbert
Schirmer described,

