00:24:23.750 --> 00:24:26.180 align:middle line:84%
of paper with the written
answers to questions

00:24:26.180 --> 00:24:30.642 align:middle line:84%
asked by those who were
present at the meetings.

00:24:30.642 --> 00:24:33.310 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:24:33.310 --> 00:24:35.820 align:middle line:90%
>>Their technology is infinite.

00:24:35.820 --> 00:24:38.010 align:middle line:90%
There were so many things I saw.

00:24:38.010 --> 00:24:40.590 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:24:40.590 --> 00:24:43.000 align:middle line:84%
>>The ones I remember the
most were the teleports.

00:24:43.000 --> 00:24:48.710 align:middle line:10%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:24:48.710 --> 00:24:52.470 align:middle line:10%
>>Their film reels or even
sometimes written notes

00:24:52.470 --> 00:24:55.210 align:middle line:10%
