00:25:07.370 --> 00:25:13.690 align:middle line:90%


00:25:13.690 --> 00:25:17.210 align:middle line:84%
>>Along with teleportation, some
of the most frequent phenomena

00:25:17.210 --> 00:25:20.170 align:middle line:84%
