00:25:43.880 --> 00:25:47.480 align:middle line:10%
So there was obviously insane
amounts of energy involved

00:25:47.480 --> 00:25:51.160 align:middle line:10%
and directivity just as crazy.

00:25:51.160 --> 00:25:54.518 align:middle line:84%
>>So I bought myself one
of those transistor radios.

00:25:54.518 --> 00:25:56.860 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:25:56.860 --> 00:25:59.400 align:middle line:84%
>>Bruno told me to, put
it there on the cabinet.

00:25:59.400 --> 00:26:01.600 align:middle line:84%
In five minutes, they'll
prepare it for you.

00:26:01.600 --> 00:26:02.770 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:26:02.770 --> 00:26:07.450 align:middle line:90%


00:26:07.450 --> 00:26:11.050 align:middle line:84%
>>In fact, after five minutes,
there was a big crack.

00:26:11.050 --> 00:26:13.210 align:middle line:84%
A sort of greenish
flame came out.

00:26:13.210 --> 00:26:14.900 align:middle line:90%
And Bruno said, there.

00:26:14.900 --> 00:26:16.640 align:middle line:90%
Now it's ready.

00:26:16.640 --> 00:26:22.015 align:middle line:10%
And they immediately greeted
me through the radio-- Sigir.

00:26:22.015 --> 00:26:24.290 align:middle line:10%
And I could also
change the frequencies.

00:26:24.290 --> 00:26:26.440 align:middle line:10%
The broadcast continued.

00:26:26.440 --> 00:26:28.390 align:middle line:10%
>>Some of these
communications were also

00:26:28.390 --> 00:26:31.960 align:middle line:10%
recorded with the reel-to-reel
devices existing then.

00:26:31.960 --> 00:26:35.020 align:middle line:84%
Gaspare still owns
some of the tapes.

00:26:35.020 --> 00:26:39.740 align:middle line:84%
For the first time after so
many years, the voice of the W56

00:26:39.740 --> 00:26:41.180 align:middle line:90%
is made public.

00:26:41.180 --> 00:26:44.680 align:middle line:10%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:26:44.680 --> 00:27:52.840 align:middle line:90%


00:27:52.840 --> 00:27:55.950 align:middle line:84%
>>Radios weren't the only
communication tools used.

00:27:55.950 --> 00:27:58.770 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes the Friends would
also insert themselves

00:27:58.770 --> 00:28:01.120 align:middle line:90%
into normal television programs.

00:28:01.120 --> 00:28:08.710 align:middle line:84%
>>I remember once there was a
film, and it was interrupted,

00:28:08.710 --> 00:28:10.752 align:middle line:84%
