00:28:10.752 --> 00:28:13.470 align:middle line:84%
while in the background
their voices,

00:28:13.470 --> 00:28:15.350 align:middle line:84%
maybe only greeting
us that time.

00:28:15.350 --> 00:28:18.940 align:middle line:90%


00:28:18.940 --> 00:28:21.150 align:middle line:84%
>>A fourth witness of
the extraordinary events

00:28:21.150 --> 00:28:24.280 align:middle line:84%
of Friendship who accepted
Breccia's invitation to speak

00:28:24.280 --> 00:28:27.390 align:middle line:84%
