00:28:33.970 --> 00:28:36.860 align:middle line:84%
Always a ufology
enthusiast, Di Girolamo

00:28:36.860 --> 00:28:40.510 align:middle line:84%
knew Consul Alberto Perego
and journalist Bruno Ghibaudi

00:28:40.510 --> 00:28:41.700 align:middle line:90%
personally.

00:28:41.700 --> 00:28:44.510 align:middle line:84%
And it was precisely the latter
to put him in touch with Bruno

00:28:44.510 --> 00:28:46.330 align:middle line:90%
Sammaccicia in Pescara.

00:28:46.330 --> 00:28:49.110 align:middle line:84%
Paolo had with him a letter
he'd written for the W56.

00:28:49.110 --> 00:28:51.830 align:middle line:90%


00:28:51.830 --> 00:28:54.530 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:28:54.530 --> 00:28:58.370 align:middle line:90%


00:28:58.370 --> 00:29:03.330 align:middle line:84%
>>And he welcomed me into a kind
of a living room, so to speak.

00:29:03.330 --> 00:29:04.230 align:middle line:90%
I enter.

00:29:04.230 --> 00:29:06.120 align:middle line:84%
I lay this letter
on the console.

00:29:06.120 --> 00:29:09.130 align:middle line:90%
And I sit down on the sofa.

00:29:09.130 --> 00:29:13.090 align:middle line:84%
At one point, Bruno
Sammaccicia says,

00:29:13.090 --> 00:29:14.610 align:middle line:90%
we should be getting some news.

00:29:14.610 --> 00:29:15.670 align:middle line:90%
Let's see.

00:29:15.670 --> 00:29:18.770 align:middle line:84%
He takes this radio
and turns it on.

00:29:18.770 --> 00:29:20.730 align:middle line:84%
The radio was playing
music, and then we

00:29:20.730 --> 00:29:25.140 align:middle line:84%
hear a piercing whistle, really
a very loud hissing sound.

00:29:25.140 --> 00:29:27.320 align:middle line:10%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:29:27.320 --> 00:29:29.080 align:middle line:10%


00:29:29.080 --> 00:29:31.610 align:middle line:10%
>>I hear Sigir here.

00:29:31.610 --> 00:29:35.710 align:middle line:10%
Hello, Paolo, be
honest with us all.

00:29:35.710 --> 00:29:37.375 align:middle line:10%
Be honest with us all.

00:29:37.375 --> 00:29:39.900 align:middle line:90%
Be honest with us all.

00:29:39.900 --> 00:29:41.990 align:middle line:90%
Three times.

00:29:41.990 --> 00:29:43.900 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:29:43.900 --> 00:29:44.700 align:middle line:90%


00:29:44.700 --> 00:29:47.290 align:middle line:84%
>>Then another voice
says, let's get the goods.

00:29:47.290 --> 00:29:49.900 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:29:49.900 --> 00:29:51.940 align:middle line:90%


00:29:51.940 --> 00:29:53.920 align:middle line:84%
>>Now, the goods
in my opinion had

00:29:53.920 --> 00:29:58.620 align:middle line:84%
to be a big parcel Sammaccicia
had taken, all lined in black

00:29:58.620 --> 00:30:00.690 align:middle line:84%
and placed on top of
the television set.

00:30:00.690 --> 00:30:05.290 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:30:05.290 --> 00:30:09.000 align:middle line:84%
>>A very loud crackle, a
real blinding purple flash,

00:30:09.000 --> 00:30:09.940 align:middle line:90%
just like that.

00:30:09.940 --> 00:30:13.510 align:middle line:90%
And then there was nothing.

00:30:13.510 --> 00:30:16.400 align:middle line:84%
>>After this event, which
leaves Paolo speechless,

00:30:16.400 --> 00:30:20.030 align:middle line:84%
the group goes out
into the street.

00:30:20.030 --> 00:30:22.060 align:middle line:84%
And when they come
back inside, Paolo

00:30:22.060 --> 00:30:24.980 align:middle line:84%
realizes that his letter,
which he'd left on the table,

00:30:24.980 --> 00:30:25.780 align:middle line:90%
was gone.

00:30:25.780 --> 00:30:28.380 align:middle line:84%
For a moment, they talk about
who might have taken it,

00:30:28.380 --> 00:30:29.960 align:middle line:90%
but nobody understands.

00:30:29.960 --> 00:30:32.730 align:middle line:84%
Sammaccicia 's wife
also denies touching it.

00:30:32.730 --> 00:30:34.950 align:middle line:84%
At that point,
Bruno urges everyone

00:30:34.950 --> 00:30:36.470 align:middle line:90%
to go out into the street again.

00:30:36.470 --> 00:30:40.190 align:middle line:90%


00:30:40.190 --> 00:30:42.250 align:middle line:10%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:30:42.250 --> 00:30:43.610 align:middle line:10%


00:30:43.610 --> 00:30:47.490 align:middle line:10%
>>There wasn't a soul in
sight at all-- around midnight

00:30:47.490 --> 00:30:49.720 align:middle line:10%
or something like that.

00:30:49.720 --> 00:30:51.370 align:middle line:90%
At a certain point, I feel--

00:30:51.370 --> 00:30:53.380 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:30:53.380 --> 00:30:54.900 align:middle line:84%
>> --something
falls on my head--

00:30:54.900 --> 00:30:57.470 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:30:57.470 --> 00:31:00.570 align:middle line:84%
>> --a little piece of
paper, all folded up.

00:31:00.570 --> 00:31:02.676 align:middle line:90%
It was a scorched envelope.

00:31:02.676 --> 00:31:04.410 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:31:04.410 --> 00:31:09.300 align:middle line:84%
>>Open, and it was the letter
I'd left on the console.

00:31:09.300 --> 00:31:12.290 align:middle line:84%
>>To make the phenomena
possible or to amplify them,

00:31:12.290 --> 00:31:15.300 align:middle line:84%
including telepathy, which
