00:31:15.300 --> 00:31:21.050 align:middle line:84%
the W56 used devices that
were called "Nuclae."

00:31:21.050 --> 00:31:23.940 align:middle line:84%
They could be placed in
objects, in rooms, or even

00:31:23.940 --> 00:31:29.560 align:middle line:84%
in the bodies of living
creatures, including people.

00:31:29.560 --> 00:31:31.876 align:middle line:10%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:31:31.876 --> 00:31:34.890 align:middle line:90%


00:31:34.890 --> 00:31:37.910 align:middle line:10%
>>These nuclae were a
necessary thing for them.

00:31:37.910 --> 00:31:40.390 align:middle line:84%
Like if I want to receive
a phone call from you,

00:31:40.390 --> 00:31:42.990 align:middle line:84%
I need to have a
phone at my house.

00:31:42.990 --> 00:31:46.010 align:middle line:84%
>>Bruno had a German
shepherd named Dick.

00:31:46.010 --> 00:31:47.890 align:middle line:84%
>>The Friends told
