00:31:47.890 --> 00:31:50.180 align:middle line:84%
would play an important
role in the contacts

00:31:50.180 --> 00:31:52.050 align:middle line:84%
and in certain
operations that called

00:31:52.050 --> 00:31:54.750 align:middle line:90%
for the help of the humans.

00:31:54.750 --> 00:31:58.560 align:middle line:84%
He would become a sort
of amplifying antenna.

00:31:58.560 --> 00:32:01.540 align:middle line:84%
So they asked Sammaccicia to
bring the dog to the seaside.

00:32:01.540 --> 00:32:10.510 align:middle line:90%


00:32:10.510 --> 00:32:13.340 align:middle line:84%
And at their command,
which came by telepathy,

00:32:13.340 --> 00:32:16.300 align:middle line:84%
Dick was made to
go into the water.

00:32:16.300 --> 00:32:20.000 align:middle line:84%
At that point, the Friends would
treat the dog placing nuclae

00:32:20.000 --> 00:32:20.843 align:middle line:90%
under his balls.

00:32:20.843 --> 00:32:24.900 align:middle line:90%


00:32:24.900 --> 00:32:29.390 align:middle line:84%
In fact, Dick was almost
always with Bruno.

00:32:29.390 --> 00:32:31.640 align:middle line:84%
In one of the film clips
that have come to light,

00:32:31.640 --> 00:32:33.390 align:middle line:84%
