out of the window

00:32:33.390 --> 00:32:35.830 align:middle line:84%
while Bruno is
filming a UFO circling

00:32:35.830 --> 00:32:39.094 align:middle line:84%
over the palazzos of Milan,
where Bruno lived for a while.

00:32:39.094 --> 00:32:42.530 align:middle line:90%


00:32:42.530 --> 00:32:45.285 align:middle line:84%
It isn't the only ufological
document made in Milan.

00:32:45.285 --> 00:32:54.880 align:middle line:90%


00:32:54.880 --> 00:32:57.630 align:middle line:84%
One of the more controversial
pieces of information that

00:32:57.630 --> 00:33:01.790 align:middle line:84%
the W56 gave to their human
Friends concerned a conflict

00:33:01.790 --> 00:33:04.790 align:middle line:84%
with an artificial race
called "Wierros(?)",

00:33:04.790 --> 00:33:08.330 align:middle line:84%
but which Sammaccicia
renamed with the term, CTR,

00:33:08.330 --> 00:33:12.620 align:middle line:84%
which was the contraction
of the word "contraries."

00:33:12.620 --> 00:33:15.660 align:middle line:10%
>>One of the strange things
about the Friendship stories

00:33:15.660 --> 00:33:20.680 align:middle line:10%
is the existence of enemies,
the famous Contrary, the CTR.

00:33:20.680 --> 00:33:24.200 align:middle line:84%
While the W56 were
ethical, these others

00:33:24.200 --> 00:33:27.080 align:middle line:84%
were materialistic,
virtually the opposite

00:33:27.080 --> 00:33:29.710 align:middle line:90%
of the W56 in every way.

00:33:29.710 --> 00:33:32.880 align:middle line:84%
They didn't speak of
war but of conflict

00:33:32.880 --> 00:33:35.280 align:middle line:84%
and said one reason
they were here

00:33:35.280 --> 00:33:37.200 align:middle line:90%
was to keep the CTR in check.

00:33:37.200 --> 00:33:39.710 align:middle line:90%


00:33:39.710 --> 00:33:42.450 align:middle line:84%
>>The Friends called
them, science worshippers,

00:33:42.450 --> 00:33:46.640 align:middle line:84%
saying the CTR were
creatures without scruples.

00:33:46.640 --> 00:33:49.010 align:middle line:84%
And their greatest
fear was that we humans

00:33:49.010 --> 00:33:53.220 align:middle line:84%
were following the same path
the CTR had already covered.

00:33:53.220 --> 00:33:56.300 align:middle line:84%
For the W56, the
feelings of Friendship,

00:33:56.300 --> 00:33:58.630 align:middle line:84%
affection, love, and
harmony that they

00:33:58.630 --> 00:34:01.440 align:middle line:84%
were creating between
themselves and the human group,

00:34:01.440 --> 00:34:03.440 align:middle line:84%
just as it is
among human beings,

00:34:03.440 --> 00:34:07.850 align:middle line:84%
were not just defining the
quality of relationships.

00:34:07.850 --> 00:34:09.840 align:middle line:10%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:34:09.840 --> 00:34:13.860 align:middle line:10%
>>For them, cohesion,
Friendship, loyalty,

00:34:13.860 --> 00:34:19.080 align:middle line:10%
and things like that are not
abstract concepts but rather

00:34:19.080 --> 00:34:23.620 align:middle line:10%
a living entity that
they call Uredda.

00:34:23.620 --> 00:34:26.969 align:middle line:84%
This living entity's
fostered precisely

00:34:26.969 --> 00:34:32.420 align:middle line:84%
by the sense of loyalty and
was contrasted by an alter ego

00:34:32.420 --> 00:34:36.040 align:middle line:84%
that what was called Redda,
which was essentially

00:34:36.040 --> 00:34:37.239 align:middle line:90%
the opposite.

00:34:37.239 --> 00:34:41.989 align:middle line:10%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:34:41.989 --> 00:34:46.270 align:middle line:10%
>>And for them, this energy
served as a sort of fuel,

00:34:46.270 --> 00:34:47.070 align:middle line:10%
let's say--

00:34:47.070 --> 00:34:49.030 align:middle line:10%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:34:49.030 --> 00:34:52.239 align:middle line:84%
>> --a driving force for some
of their means of defense--

00:34:52.239 --> 00:34:54.260 align:middle line:90%
>>[SPEAKING ITALIAN]

00:34:54.260 --> 00:34:57.110 align:middle line:90%
>> --or anyway, for their tools.

00:34:57.110 --> 00:34:59.510 align:middle line:84%
>>The defense instruments
Gaspare talks about,

00:34:59.510 --> 00:35:01.740 align:middle line:84%
the Friends explained,
were also important

00:35:01.740 --> 00:35:05.840 align:middle line:84%
for the conflict they
had with the CTR.

00:35:05.840 --> 00:35:09.770 align:middle line:84%
They explained that Friendship,
which Uredda originated from,

00:35:09.770 --> 00:35:12.220 align:middle line:84%
was so important that
if the group hadn't kept

00:35:12.220 --> 00:35:15.770 align:middle line:84%
the harmony high, or if the
group was even dismembered,

00:35:15.770 --> 00:35:17.160 align:middle line:84%
they themselves
would have fallen

00:35:17.160 --> 00:35:19.810 align:middle line:84%
victims of the
CTR, who might well

00:35:19.810 --> 00:35:22.580 align:middle line:90%
have destroyed their bases.

00:35:22.580 --> 00:35:26.370 align:middle line:84%
But this wasn't the only
reason to be Friends.

00:35:26.370 --> 00:35:30.300 align:middle line:84%
The W56 said that love in
its most unselfish sense,

00:35:30.300 --> 00:35:33.840 align:middle line:84%
as well as ethics,
respect, and altruism,

00:35:33.840 --> 00:35:37.270 align:middle line:84%
should guide every
thought and every action.

00:35:37.270 --> 00:35:39.760 align:middle line:84%
They said these values
were essential to ensure

00:35:39.760 --> 00:35:44.400 align:middle line:84%
a safe and healthy
evolutionary progress,

00:35:44.400 --> 00:35:47.590 align:middle line:84%
a lesson that humanity had to
put into practice if it wanted

00:35:47.590 --> 00:35:51.360 align:middle line:84%
to avoid the risk of
terrible self-destruction.

00:35:51.360 --> 00:35:55.890 align:middle line:84%
The mere thought of doing harm
was inconceivable to the W56.

00:35:55.890 --> 00:35:58.080 align:middle line:84%
And the sense of
ethics, morality

00:35:58.080 --> 00:36:01.910 align:middle line:84%
pervaded their every
action, their every gesture,

00:36:01.910 --> 00:36:03.670 align:middle line:90%
their every thought.

00:36:03.670 --> 00:36:06.070 align:middle line:84%
Even their technology,
their machines,

00:36:06.070 --> 00:36:09.850 align:middle line:84%
were consciously impregnated
with it, a concept

00:36:09.850 --> 00:36:11.330 align:middle line:90%
that for us is unimaginable.

00:36:11.330 --> 00:36:16.670 align:middle line:90%


00:36:16.670 --> 00:36:20.680 align:middle line:10%
>>They said they were incapable
of causing harm to anyone.

00:36:20.680 --> 00:36:23.100 align:middle line:10%
They said that even
their very devices

00:36:23.100 --> 00:36:25.610 align:middle line:10%
would refuse to harm anyone.

00:36:25.610 --> 00:36:28.910 align:middle line:84%
Ethics permeated everything
about them to the point

00:36:28.910 --> 00:36:30.680 align:middle line:90%
that they would refuse.

00:36:30.680 --> 00:36:33.220 align:middle line:84%
Indeed, they said
that if they weren't

00:36:33.220 --> 00:36:36.200 align:middle line:84%
able to avoid harming
someone, then in that case

00:36:36.200 --> 00:36:38.940 align:middle line:90%
they would self-destruct.

00:36:38.940 --> 00:36:42.000 align:middle line:84%
>>It wasn't by chance that
